    ```bash  theme={null}
    npm install @x402/hono @x402/core @x402/evm @x402/svm
    ```
  </Tab>

  <Tab title="Go">
    Add the x402 Go module to your project:

    ```bash  theme={null}
    go get github.com/coinbase/x402/go
    ```
  </Tab>

